Package de.hshannover.dqgui.framework.api

Interface Manageable

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Loadable, Registrable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Views
    public interface Manageable
extends Loadable, Registrable
    Marker interface combining Loadable and Registrable.

    All keys that map to a view that shall be managed by the ApplicationContext must implement this.

    A Manageable must implement a working Object.hashCode() and Object.equals(Object).
